.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
Increase version from \f(CR1.0.2\fP to \f(CR2.0.0\fP.
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ git bump\-version \-\-major
.fi
.if n .RE
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
